sentences: Rena Jones (born 1977) is an American musician, producer and audio engineer from Portland, Oregon.
Her latest album titled Echoes was released in April 2013.
From 2000 to 2002 she studied sound engineering at Ex'pression College for Digital Arts in Emeryville, California.
In 2007 she moved to Portland, Oregon.
Two of Jones's albums, Driftwood and Indra's Web, were listed among Echoes radio's top 25 albums of the year in 2006 and 2009, respectively.
